  "title": "Project Coordinator (Interior Fit-Out & Carpentry) #79039",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building & Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Project Coordinator (Interior Fit-Out & Carpentry)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Depending on project site</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 9AM-6PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + VB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate and monitor project progress, workmanship quality, and compliance with</li><li>contractual requirements.</li><li>Liaise with subcontractors on all project-related matters.</li><li>Communicate effectively with clients and manage expectations throughout the project.</li><li>Oversee quality control processes to ensure adherence to specifications and industry</li><li>standards.</li><li>Manage project closeout activities, including final inspections, documentation, and handover</li><li>to clients.</li><li>Foster good team morale and teamwork within the project team.</li><li>Ensure safety regulations are strictly observed at all work sites.</li><li>Perform other ad hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience in site coordination and project management.</li><li>Knowledge of Interior Design, Carpentry, or Joinery is preferred.</li><li>Able to work independently in a fast-paced environment with minimal supervision.</li><li>Minimum 2–3 years of relevant working experience.</li><li>Able to commence work within short notice is an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79039 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
